Brave-style overlay directory.

Files placed here mirror the Chromium source tree structure.
During build, apply_overlays.py copies them into the source tree,
replacing the originals.

Example:
  chromium_src/chrome/browser/profiles/profile.cc
  -> replaces build/src/chrome/browser/profiles/profile.cc

This is preferred over patches for file-level replacements since
overlay files don't break on Chromium version bumps the way patches do.
The build will simply fail to compile if the API changes, which is
easier to debug than a failed patch application.
